lass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104coz1665702802235.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/coz1665702802235.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/coz1665702802235.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"coz1665702802235\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Signature\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the Signature Editor (Define Signature) to create or edit the signatures for Uniface and non-Uniface components.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"coz1665702802235__p_d6074e1_d6075e1_d6076e1\">To compile a signature, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Compile Signature</span></span>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"coz1665702802235__section_iwb_h2f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d135145e64\">Buttons</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"coz1665702802235__ul_sgv_h2f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3008e1_d3009e1_d3010e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allow Edit</span>—enable\n               entity-level signatures to be edited or deleted. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"coz1665702802235__note_wgv_h2f_5cc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> We recommend that you do not use the Signature Editor to manage\n                  entity-level signatures. By default, it is not possible to modify or delete\n                  entity-level signatures. If you must do so, first click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allow\n                     Edit</span>.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3011e1_d3012e1_d3013e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Properties</span>—define signature\n               properties, including the call-in properties of a component. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3014e1_d3015e1_d3016e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">+</span> —add an operation or\n               parameter to the signature </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3017e1_d3018e1_d3019e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">&gt;&gt;</span>—display and other\n               dialog box in which you can select an item or define additional properties </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"coz1665702802235__section_zfb_32f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d135145e99\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"coz1665702802235__ul_sf2_j2f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3020e1_d3021e1_d3022e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3023e1_d3024e1_d3025e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rki1665702802443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rki1665702802443.html\" title=\"List of implementations described by the signature.\">Implementations</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3026e1_d3027e1_d3028e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3029e1_d3030e1_d3031e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cui1665702579786.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cui1665702579786.html\" title=\"Operations for the current component.\">Operation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3032e1_d3033e1_d3034e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kvh1665702802512.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kvh1665702802512.html\" title=\"Enter comments about the operation that is selected in the Operation field.\">Comments (tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3035e1_d3036e1_d3037e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dit1665702802582.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dit1665702802582.html\" title=\"User documentation for the operation pre-conditions.\">Pre-Conditions</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3038e1_d3039e1_d3040e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"drv1665702802652.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/drv1665702802652.html\" title=\"User documentation for the operation's post conditions.\">Post-Conditions</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3041e1_d3042e1_d3043e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zkx1665702802723.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zkx1665702802723.html\" title=\"User documentation for the operation's return value.\">Return Value</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3044e1_d3045e1_d3046e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fjd1665702802791.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fjd1665702802791.html\" title=\"Parameters that exist for the selected operation.\">Parameter</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3047e1_d3048e1_d3049e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wlc1665702802859.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wlc1665702802859.html\" title=\"Direction of the selected operation parameter.\">In/Out</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3050e1_d3051e1_d3052e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nkv1665702792163.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nkv1665702792163.html\" title=\"Data type of the selected parameter. The default value is String.\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"coz1665702802235__p_d6083e1_d6084e1_d6085e1\">For Uniface components, the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comments</span> fields are not\n            overwritten when the component is compiled using the component editor.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"coz1665702802235__section_zpk_k2f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d135145e220\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"coz1665702802235__ul_lrq_k2f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3053e1_d3054e1_d3055e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zzx1665702678830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zzx1665702678830.html\" title=\"Use the Signature Editor to create or modify component signatures. Signatures of Uniface components are automatically generated during compilation. Signatures of non-Uniface components can be created or imported.\">Define a Component Signature</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3056e1_d3057e1_d3058e1\">To define the properties of a signature, click the\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Properties</span> button. This also enables you to maintain the\n               call-in properties of a component. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"coz1665702802235__li_d3059e1_d3060e1_d3061e1\">To modify entity-level signatures, click\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allow Edit</span>, then choose the desired action from the\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span> menu. (When performing\n               global updates, it is not necessary to first click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allow\n               Edit</span>.) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526554\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526554\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Signature Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Signature Use the Signature Editor (Define Signature) to create or edit the signatures for Uniface and non-Uniface components. To compile a signature, choose File >Compile Signature . Buttons Allow Edit —enable entity-level signatures to be edited or deleted. Note: We recommend that you do not use the Signature Editor to manage entity-level signatures. By default, it is not possible to modify or delete entity-level signatures. If you must do so, first click Allow Edit . Properties —define signature properties, including the call-in properties of a component. + —add an operation or parameter to the signature >> —display and other dialog box in which you can select an item or define additional properties Fields Description Implementations Comments Operation Comments (tab) Pre-Conditions Post-Conditions Return Value Parameter In/Out Data Type For Uniface components, the Description and Comments fields are not overwritten when the component is compiled using the component editor. How to Define a Component Signature To define the properties of a signature, click the Properties button. This also enables you to maintain the call-in properties of a component. To modify entity-level signatures, click Allow Edit , then choose the desired action from the File or Edit menu. (When performing global updates, it is not necessary to first click Allow Edit .) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}